dnl Process this file with autoconf to produce a configure script.
AC_REVISION($Id$)dnl

AC_PREREQ(2.58)

dnl ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
dnl
dnl Top-level configure.in for wxWidgets by Robert Roebling, Phil Blecker,
dnl Vadim Zeitlin and Ron Lee
dnl
