dnl Check for headers
dnl ------------------------------------------------------------------------

dnl Note: non-empty last parameter makes check compile-only,
dnl   skipping worthless preprocessing check
AC_CHECK_HEADERS(langinfo.h wchar.h,,, [AC_INCLUDES_DEFAULT])

